nodes.text: The Last Jedi: Rose Tico: Resistance Fighter

The Last Jedi: Rose Tico: Resistance Fighter is a reference book based on Star Wars: Episode VIII The Last Jedi from Studio Fun International. Written by Jason Fry, the book was released on May 1, 2018.
Follow the next adventure in the Star Wars saga in this first person narrative.
This book for tweens will feature a first-person account from one of the main characters of the second installment in the Star Wars sequel trilogy. Format includes foldouts.
The book was originally titled Rose Tico: My Resistance.
